<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<div class="call-to-action">
<h2 id="stay-up-to-date">Stay up to date</h2>

<p>The UK will leave the EU on 31 October. This page tells you how to prepare for Brexit. It will be updated if anything changes, including if a deal is agreed.<br></br></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/government/brexit">Sign up for email alerts</a> to get the latest information.</p>
</div>

<p>The UK will remain in the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/what-you-need-to-move-goods-between-or-through-common-transit-countries-including-the-eu">Common Transit Convention (CTC)</a> after Brexit.</p>

<div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
<p>In a no-deal Brexit, you can go to alternative government offices of destination and departure if you’re travelling through the Port of Dover and Eurotunnel.</p>
</div>

<p>If these alternative sites are full, you might be diverted to another location. The police or Highways England will let you know if there are any diversions.</p>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://highwaysengland.co.uk/OperationBrock/">Check if any diversions are in place</a> before you travel to the port on Highways England’s website.</p>

<p>If diversions are in place to manage freight traffic on the major roads leading to the Port of Dover, you will need to go to:</p>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

     Manston Airport
<br></br>     Manston Road
<br></br>     Ramsgate 
<br></br>     Kent
<br></br>     CT12 5BQ
<br></br>     
</p></div></div>

<p>Manston Airport is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>

<p>If traffic management systems in Kent - known as Operation Brock - are activated, border readiness checks will take place in traffic queues.</p>

<p>If you’re a haulier and do not have all the correct documents to cross the border, you’ll be told to go to a holding site in Ashford or Manston Airport. Once you get there, you will have a limited period to establish what you need to do to be able to cross the border.</p>

<h2 id="importing-goods-through-the-port-of-dover">Importing goods through the Port of Dover</h2>

<p>If you’re not ending the movement of your goods at an authorised consignee’s premises, go to the office of destination at Dover Western Docks:</p>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

     Dover Western Docks
<br></br>     Lord Warden Square 
<br></br>     Dover 
<br></br>     CT17 9TF
<br></br>     
</p></div></div>

<p>Dover Western Docks is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>

<h2 id="importing-goods-through-eurotunnel">Importing goods through Eurotunnel</h2>

<p>If you’re not ending the movement of your goods at an authorised consignee’s premises, go to the office of destination at Ashford International Truck Stop:</p>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

     Ashford International Truck Stop 
<br></br>     Waterbrook Avenue
<br></br>     Ashford
<br></br>     TN24 0GB
<br></br>     
</p></div></div>

<p>Ashford International Truck Stop is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>

<h2 id="exporting-through-the-port-of-dover-and-eurotunnel">Exporting through the Port of Dover and Eurotunnel</h2>

<p>If you’re not starting the movement of your goods at an authorised consignor’s premises, go to the office of departure at either:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="#north-weald">North Weald Airfield</a></li>
  <li><a href="#ebbsfleet">Ebbsfleet International Rail Station car park D</a></li>
  <li><a href="#stop24">Stop 24</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="north-weald">North Weald Airfield</h3>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

North Weald Airfield
<br></br>     Merlin Way
<br></br>     North Weald Bassett
<br></br>     Epping
<br></br>     CM16 6HR
<br></br>     
</p></div></div>

<p>North Weald Airfield is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>

<h3 id="ebbsfleet">Ebbsfleet International Station</h3>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

     Ebbsfleet International Rail Station car park D
<br></br>     International Way
<br></br>     Ebbsfleet Valley
<br></br>     DA10 1EB
<br></br>     
</p></div></div>

<p>Ebbsfleet International Rail Station is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>

<h3 id="stop24">Stop 24</h3>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

     Stop 24
<br></br>     Folkestone Services 
<br></br>     15 Ashford Road 
<br></br>     Hythe
<br></br>     CT21 4BL
<br></br>     
</p></div></div>

<p>Stop 24 is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>

</div>
</div>


